          <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
          <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          "I am very happy with my new roof. I expected a difficult time with the insurance company but Riley dealt with reporting the damage and getting approval for the replacement. The crew worked their tails off and completed the work and clean up. Thank you!"
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
            BP
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Bruce P.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Homeowner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 - Cade Jensen -->
